522
00:58:10.830 --> 00:58:19.500
Enis Elezi: If I'm going to interview, let's say, 6 staff members in my organization, do I need to get content from my management, or just those 6 people individually? Well, both.

523
00:58:19.650 --> 00:58:36.640
Enis Elezi: First of all, you need a constant letter, or an email would be sufficient if… an email would be sufficient from your line manager, or someone of a senior role than you, or your line manager, saying that they're happy to support Wilson in undertaking their research.

524
00:58:37.050 --> 00:58:44.540
